'''Rino Romano''' (born [[1960s#1969|1969]]) is an Italian-Canadian voice actor whose most well-known roles are those of Bruce Wayne/Batman in ''The Batman'', opposite [[Kevin Michael Richardson]], Darien Shields/Tuxedo Mask in the early episodes of the DiC dubbed anime ''Sailor Moon'' and Lone Starr in ''Spaceballs: The Animated Series''. In the Star Wars universe, he provided the voices of [[Kyle Katarn]] in ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith]]'' and [[Firith Me]] and the male [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] (taunts and replies in player's commands) in ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''.
